StorageSettings
Defines the settings for a StorageContainer The following are default settings, and are applied automatically if a Container is created without modifying the settings: - Use Cache: true - Cache on Retrieve: true - Cache on Store: true - Cache Duration: 1 minute - Flush Rate: 5 minutes - Flush Cooldown: 5 seconds Some containers will change these default settings.
Stored
Annotates a field as a field that can be stored and/or retrieved from using a StorageDecomposer If a field is being used as a recompose field as well, it must be in the same order that the RecomposeConstructor's parameters are defined in.

Hooks into a StorageContainer to specify how the StorageContainer should store data to the data structure.
